snippet.title: Sature Trailer
snippet.description:
Sature is a strategy board game of color for mobile and desktop platforms.

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...
Apple's App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id938010796
itch.io (PC/Mac/Linux): https://iansundstrom.itch.io/sature

For more information visit http://www.herringbonegames.com/sature.html

Facebook: facebook.com/saturegame
Twitter: @iansundstrom
